thread.title: David

author: David
title: David
text: Jumped on your site by accident best mistake I ever made. I was looking for a seat protector cover for our dog who comes everywhere with us. No only had you got it in stock but at a great price. Was able to purchase on line and less than 5 minutes later I got a text saying I could collect it Immediately. Colin was a great help. Will definitely recommend mocks garage. com to evefyone
